I lost a contact lens.

213
00:17:41,025 --> 00:17:42,018
What?

214
00:17:42,105 --> 00:17:43,415
I lost a lens.

215
00:17:44,385 --> 00:17:46,535
I'll look for it later.
Can we just do with one?

216
00:17:46,625 --> 00:17:48,776
I can't see without it,
and it cost me 85 bucks!

217
00:17:48,866 --> 00:17:50,623
I'll lend you the money, for God's sake.

218
00:17:50,705 --> 00:17:52,179
Oh, my... I found it.

219
00:17:53,346 --> 00:17:55,016
Get it. Come on, let's go.

220
00:18:05,427 --> 00:18:06,377
Well...

221
00:18:08,988 --> 00:18:10,265
See you later.

222
00:18:21,989 --> 00:18:23,299
He's gonna blow it.

223
00:18:23,789 --> 00:18:25,099
He's gonna blow it.

224
00:18:25,189 --> 00:18:26,347
Stay with him.

225
00:18:26,429 --> 00:18:27,947
Don't forget the guys we're after

226
00:18:28,029 --> 00:18:30,180
put a little old lady in the hospital.

227
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:32,704
I can't believe the lieutenant
would let a screw-up like Sleigh

228
00:18:32,789 --> 00:18:34,187
work this kind of stakeout.

229
00:18:34,270 --> 00:18:36,464
The lieutenant's been
under a lot of pressure lately.

230
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:38,461
Yeah? What kind of pressure?

231
00:18:38,550 --> 00:18:39,620
Sleigh.

232
00:18:39,711 --> 00:18:41,784
He's been driving the lieutenant bananas.

233
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:45,385
Maybe he hopes Sleigh will
end up like the little old lady.

234
00:18:45,471 --> 00:18:46,705
Come on.

235
00:18:46,791 --> 00:18:50,262
To tell you the truth, that thought
has passed through my mind.

236
00:18:53,472 --> 00:18:56,343
Stop! Stop! Back up, back up, back up!

237
00:19:00,193 --> 00:19:03,543
Stop! Stop! Go forward. Go forward.

238
00:19:04,673 --> 00:19:06,026
Now, stop!

239
00:19:08,514 --> 00:19:10,151
Hi there, beautiful.

240
00:19:10,913 --> 00:19:12,431
Pardon me, I...

241
00:19:13,634 --> 00:19:15,632
I feel that I know you.

242
00:19:15,714 --> 00:19:17,471
Are you by any chance...

243
00:19:18,435 --> 00:19:21,785
Sheila Swanhill from Petoskey, Michigan?

244
