Did you know that Petoskey
is the cement capital of the world?

251
00:19:49,757 --> 00:19:51,427
Some drunk's trying to pick him up.

252
00:19:52,197 --> 00:19:55,832
She had a cousin named...

253
00:19:59,239 --> 00:20:00,592
Lindtrude.

254
00:20:01,199 --> 00:20:02,989
My name's Derina.

255
00:20:04,039 --> 00:20:08,350
Derina!

256
00:20:08,440 --> 00:20:10,557
You have a lovely voice.

257
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:13,554
You do

258
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:15,834
Something to me

259
00:20:16,441 --> 00:20:18,351
Something that

260
00:20:18,440 --> 00:20:21,431
Simply mystifies me

261
00:20:21,521 --> 00:20:23,475
Tell me

262
00:20:23,561 --> 00:20:25,515
Why should it be

263
00:20:25,601 --> 00:20:28,952
You have the power to hypnotize me?

264
00:20:30,922 --> 00:20:32,275
It's getting out of hand.

